---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof vs Ryviu — Shopify reviews app vs flexible testimonial widget | SocialProof" description="Ryviu is a Shopify product reviews app. SocialProof collects testimonials that work on any website platform. Compare features, pricing, and fit." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/vs/ryviu">
<style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #fff; color: #111; }
    nav { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
    nav a.logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #111; text-decoration: none; }
    nav .nav-links a { margin-left: 1.5rem; color: #555; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    nav .cta-nav { background: #111; color: #fff !important; padding: .45rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .hero { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .vs-badge { display: inline-block; background: #f0f0f0; color: #555; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: .35rem .75rem; border-radius: 99px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
    .hero h1 span { color: #4f46e5; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; color: #444; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }
    .hero-cta { display: inline-block; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    .price-callout { display: inline-flex; gap: 2rem; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.25rem 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .price-callout .item { text-align: center; }
    .price-callout .item .price { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .price-callout .item .label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #777; margin-top: .2rem; }
    .price-callout .item.vouch .price { color: #4f46e5; }
    .price-callout .item.other .price { color: #dc2626; }
    section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .compare-table th { padding: .75rem 1rem; text-align: left; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; color: #888; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; }
    .compare-table th:nth-child(2) { color: #4f46e5; }
    .compare-table td { padding: .85rem 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; font-size: 0.97rem; vertical-align: top; }
    .compare-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .compare-table td:first-child { color: #555; font-weight: 500; }
    .yes { color: #16a34a; font-weight: 600; }
    .no { color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; }
    .partial { color: #d97706; font-weight: 600; }
    .winner-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .winner-card { border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.75rem; }
    .winner-card.vouch { background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #86efac; }
    .winner-card.other { background: #fafafa; border: 1px solid #e5e5e5; }
    .winner-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 0 0 .75rem; }
    .winner-card ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; }
    .winner-card li { font-size: 0.92rem; color: #444; margin-bottom: .4rem; }
    .savings-box { background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fcd34d; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .savings-box h3 { margin: 0 0 .5rem; font-size: 1rem; }
    .savings-box p { margin: 0; color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .bottom-cta { text-align: center; background: #4f46e5; color: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 3.5rem 2rem; margin: 3rem 0; }
    .bottom-cta h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .bottom-cta p { color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .bottom-cta a { background: #fff; color: #4f46e5; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem; }
    footer { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; color: #888; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    @media(max-width:600px) { .price-callout { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; } .winner-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
<nav>
  <a href="/" class="logo">SocialProof</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/for">Solutions</a>
    <a href="/vs">Comparisons</a>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="cta-nav">Try Free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <span class="vs-badge">SocialProof vs Ryviu</span>
  <h1>Shopify-only reviews<br/>vs <span>testimonials everywhere.</span></h1>
  <p>Ryviu is a Shopify reviews app that lives inside your product pages. SocialProof is a testimonial platform that embeds anywhere — your Shopify store, your landing pages, your booking site, your email. Your testimonials should go wherever your customers are.</p>
  <div class="price-callout">
    <div class="item vouch"><div class="price">Free</div><div class="label">SocialProof to start</div></div>
    <div class="item other"><div class="price">$9+</div><div class="label">Ryviu per month</div></div>
  </div>
  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="hero-cta">Start free with SocialProof →</a>
</div>

<section>
  <h2>Shopify-native vs. platform-agnostic</h2>
  <p>Ryviu integrates directly with Shopify's product review schema — great if all your sales happen through Shopify product pages. It imports reviews from AliExpress, sends review request emails, and shows star ratings in Google Shopping. If you're a pure Shopify dropshipper, it's purpose-built for that workflow.</p>
  <p>SocialProof is platform-agnostic. You paste one script tag and your testimonial widget appears anywhere: Shopify, Squarespace, Webflow, WordPress, Framer, or a hand-coded HTML page. More importantly, SocialProof collects text testimonials from any customer — not just Shopify buyers.</p>

  <table class="compare-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Feature</th><th>SocialProof</th><th>Ryviu</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Starting price</td><td class="yes">Free forever (1 widget)</td><td class="partial">Free plan (limited), paid from $9/mo</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Works on non-Shopify sites</td><td class="yes">Yes — any platform</td><td class="no">No — Shopify only</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Direct testimonial collection</td><td class="yes">Yes — collection link</td><td class="partial">Only from Shopify order buyers</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Approval before publishing</td><td class="yes">Full control</td><td class="partial">Moderation available</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Embed on landing pages</td><td class="yes">Yes — any page</td><td class="no">Shopify pages only</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Works for service businesses</td><td class="yes">Yes</td><td class="no">No — product reviews only</td></tr>
      <tr><td>AliExpress review import</td><td class="no">No</td><td class="yes">Yes</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Multi-platform embed</td><td class="yes">Yes — unlimited pages</td><td class="no">Shopify only</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="winner-grid">
    <div class="winner-card vouch">
      <h3>✅ Choose SocialProof if…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>You need testimonials on landing pages outside Shopify</li>
        <li>You're a service or digital product business</li>
        <li>You want testimonials from all customers, not just Shopify buyers</li>
        <li>You're on Squarespace, Webflow, WordPress, or Framer</li>
        <li>You want approval control before anything goes live</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="winner-card other">
      <h3>Consider Ryviu if…</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>You're running a Shopify dropshipping store</li>
        <li>You need AliExpress review import</li>
        <li>You want product-level star ratings in Google Shopping</li>
        <li>All your social proof lives inside Shopify product pages</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="savings-box">
    <h3>🛒 Using Shopify? SocialProof still works there too</h3>
    <p>SocialProof embeds on Shopify just fine — paste the widget script into a custom HTML section. The difference: your testimonials also work on your landing pages, email newsletters, and any other channel. You're not locked into Shopify's ecosystem.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="bottom-cta">
    <h2>Testimonials that go everywhere your customers do.</h2>
    <p>Collect testimonials from any customer on any platform, and embed them anywhere. Free forever for 1 active widget — no credit card required.</p>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup">Get started free →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2025 SocialProof · <a href="/vs" style="color:#888">More comparisons</a> · <a href="/" style="color:#888">Home</a></p>
</footer>

<div class="footer-links" style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:0.9rem;">
  <strong style="color:#374151;">Also explore:</strong>
  <a href="/for/coaches" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Coaches</a>
  <a href="/for/freelancers" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Freelancers</a>
  <a href="/for/ecommerce" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Ecommerce</a>
  <a href="/vs/senja" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Senja</a>
  <a href="/vs/testimonial" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Testimonial.to</a>
</div>
</Base>
